      <h2>High-Tension Wire Gopher Traps</h2>
      <p>These are my first pick on almost every job. High-tension stainless steel wire traps — the Macabee style and the Cinch style — are built for the main tunnel lines where the gopher is actually traveling. You’re not hoping the gopher wanders into something. You’re cutting off the freeway.</p>
